I am collaborating with Dr. Cassie Ettinger, a microbial ecologist, to understand how the soil rhizosphere community shifts when native plants compete with invasive plants, and whether these shifts reinforce invader dominance. Our paper on this topic is currently under review in Microbiome, but you can read about it here.
